      <section eId="sec_CCP-86">
        <num>CCP 86</num>
        <heading>86. Â Action involving voting trusts</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-86__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>In the parish or parishes where the document or documents creating the voting trust were executed.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-86__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>If stock transferred to the voting trust was held by an inter vivos trust, in the parish or parishes where the inter vivos trust documents were executed.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-86__subsec_3">
          <num>(3)</num>
          <content>
            <p>If stock transferred to the voting trust was held by a mortis causa trust, in the parish having jurisdiction over the settlor's estate.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112279</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
